jira
Class Jira

java.lang.Object
  jira.Jira

public class Jira
extends java.lang.Object

Class to parse information from an online jira source. Uses Gson models found in db.models.jira and then populates the SocialDb database with the information.
This is also the entry point for linking Between Jira communication and changesets in the TechnicalDb

Author:
braden
See Also:
SocialDb, TechnicalDb, Gson
